data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This remodeled 3 beds 2.5 bath, 2 car garage townhome in the gated community of Magnolia Park is a steal! All top-of-the-line appliances are included, washer and dryer as well.  Functional Layout of the first floor has an open kitchen with granite countertops, pantry, storage room, powder room, and a covered patio with sliding glass. The second floor has a nice-sized loft area with additional storage. The master suite has a huge walk-in closet, double sink, soaker tub and shower bath. There is a second bedroom with walk in closet, a third bedroom, laundry room, and a remodeled full bathroom on this second floor. Included in HOA are water/sewer bill, water/landscaping maintenance, exterior paint, roof, full access to all 3 community pools, playground, splash bad, and basketball court. Home is equipped with solar panels which will significantly reduce you electric bill.  Taexx pest system is incorporated into the walls and sellers had pest control service since the purchase. Come see this home and  BRING ALL OFFERS!
